    FunctionSetBuilder implements the basis set and spline builder for the following types of splines:

    Exponential basis tension splines Hyperbolic basis tension splines Polynomial basis splines Bernstein Polynomial basis splines Kaklis Pandelis basis tension splines This elastic coefficients for the segment using Ck basis splines inside [0,...,1) - Globally [x_0,...,x_1) are extracted for: y = Estimator (Ck, x) * ShapeControl (x) where x is the normalized ordinate mapped as x becomes (x - x_i-1) / (x_i - x_i-1) The inverse quadratic/rational spline is a typical shape controller spline used.
